Weather analysis

Getting data

We're going to use the cism package to get weather data for the FQMA weather station (Maputo).

library(cism)
library(data.table)
??get_weather

Getting data

weather <- get_weather(station = 'FQMA', 
                       start_year = 2010,
                       end_year = 2017)

Introducing the dplyr package

dplyr is very useful

library(dplyr)

Get the average temperature per month

x <- 
  weather %>%
  group_by(month) %>%
  summarise(average_temperature = mean(temp_mean, na.rm = TRUE))

Visualization of average temperature

plot(x = x$month,
     y = x$average_temperature)
